%% seq_08_project_management.mmd
%% Scope: Project management overview.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_08a_project_create_member_add.mmd
%%   - seq_08b_project_delete.mmd
%% Note:
%%   - TransferProjectOwnershipCommand exists but no route is wired, so it is omitted here.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Org Member
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: CREATE OR GROW PROJECT
    U->>B: Submit project form or add member
    B->>C: POST /projects or POST /projects/members
    C->>Cmd: CreateProjectCommand or AddProjectMemberCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Persist project or member record
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit project:created or project:member_added
    C-->>B: Redirect back

    Note over U, Evt: DELETE PROJECT
    U->>B: Delete project
    B->>C: DELETE /projects/:id
    C->>Cmd: DeleteProjectCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Validate blockers and soft delete project
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit project:deleted
    C-->>B: Redirect to projects list
